                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="gruffy"></a>Gruffy Fayre 10th June from 12.30pm</h3>
                <p>Sanderstead's Gruffy Fayre run by the 16th Purley Scouts will be held on 10th June, opening at 12.30 pm on the Gruffy beside Sanderstead pond. Stalls include Bouncy Castle, Octupus Ride, Face Painting, Cub 5 aside football, All Saints Church, Sanderstead Guides, Cake Stall, Pimms Tent and much more.</p>
              </td>
