                <p>There are two more work days scheduled before the summer break. JUNE 10th and JULY 22nd.  Last year’s July’s picnic turned into a very enjoyable BBQ and that is what is planned for this July, please put these dates in diaries</p>
               
               <p>For further information please email or call Stanley Lowy: 020 8657 3684 or stanlowy@outlook.com, Elizabeth Bennett: bennett_e@sky.com, or Mac Court mac@skyy.me.uk</p>
              </td>
              <td class="events"><h3><%= link_to image_tag("small-images/purley_beeches100.jpg", alt: "Purley Beeches logo"), "/resource/purley_beeches_enrol.pdf" %></h3>
